OL,3,CCutting deep: Welsh Rugby faces
OL,4,Cradical reform to reverse sport's
OL,5,Cdecline
OL,7,FThere is a desperate battle brewing in
OL,8,Fthe proud rugby nation of Wales, with
OL,9,Fa U-turn by the Welsh Rugby Union
OL,10,Fthrowing the game into chaos. ITV News
OL,11,FWales Reporter Rhys Williams has more
OL,13,FHaving punched above its weight for so
OL,14,Flong, Wales has worn its rugby
OL,15,Fheritage like a badge of honour.
