OL,3,CCutting deep: Welsh Rugby faces
OL,4,Cradical reform to reverse sport's
OL,5,Cdecline
OL,7,FBut after a string of disappointing
OL,8,Fresults on the pitch, resignations in
OL,9,Fthe governing body over allegations of
OL,10,Fmisogyny and sexism, and a growing
OL,11,Ffinancial crisis, the future of Welsh
OL,12,Frugby has never looked more uncertain.
OL,14,FJust months after pledging to fund the
OL,15,Fexisting four professional clubs, the
OL,16,FWelsh Rugby Union is now considering a
OL,17,Fradical and controversial
OL,18,Frestructuring of the professional
OL,19,Fgame, including the possibility of
OL,20,Fhalving the number of clubs from four
OL,21,Fto just two.
