OL,3,CCutting deep: Welsh Rugby faces
OL,4,Cradical reform to reverse sport's
OL,5,Cdecline
OL,7,FIt's a move that would reshape the
OL,8,Fsport at its highest level in Wales,
OL,9,Fbut one that's already causing anger
OL,10,Fand resentment among thousands of
OL,11,Fsupporters.
OL,13,FIt has also created enormous
OL,14,Funcertainty for the clubs, with the
OL,15,Fnew season due to begin next month.
