OL,3,CCutting deep: Welsh Rugby faces
OL,4,Cradical reform to reverse sport's
OL,5,Cdecline
OL,7,FIt would be a very bold move. No
OL,8,Finternational team with fewer than
OL,9,Ffour professional clubs has even
OL,10,Ffinished higher than third in the Six
OL,11,FNations Rugby Championship, let alone
OL,12,Fwin it.
OL,14,FWRU CEO Abi Tierney told ITV News
OL,15,Ftoday that this is a "once-in-a-
OL,16,Fgeneration chance to get this right
OL,17,Ffor Wales", and acknowledged the
OL,18,Furgent need to provide stability and
OL,19,Fclarity to the game.
