OL,7,FNeath MP and Swansea East MP Carolyn
OL,8,FHarris has hit back strongly, calling
OL,9,Ftheir behaviour "underhand."
OL,11,FCarolyn Harris says she is
OL,12,F'incandescent' at the intervention of
OL,13,Fpoliticians from Carmarthenshire for
OL,14,Ftrying to 'take things into their own
OL,15,Fhands'
