OL,3,CCutting deep: Welsh Rugby faces
OL,4,Cradical reform to reverse sport's
OL,5,Cdecline
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Ospreys CEO Lance Bradley
OL,8,Ftold ITV News that it's vital the
OL,9,Fclubs know what's happening "as soon
OL,10,Fas we can," but said short-term pain
OL,11,Fcould be worth it if it leads to long-
OL,12,Fterm gain for Welsh rugby.
OL,14,F"We have to keep our eye on the prize
OL,15,Fhere. What we're all aiming for is to
OL,16,Fget Welsh rugby, at both national and
OL,17,Fclub level, into a much better place
OL,18,Fthan it is now. That's what we're all
OL,19,Fworking together to try and achieve."
