OL,7,F"Whatever happens, we're very positive
OL,8,Fabout the future here at St Helen's
OL,9,Fand to be honest, we can't wait to be
OL,10,Fin."
OL,12,FThe landscape of Welsh rugby looks set
OL,13,Fto change dramatically. The hope is
OL,14,Fthat bold reform can reverse its
OL,15,Fdecline.
OL,17,FBut the fear remains: cutting teams
OL,18,Fmay only make things worse.
